{
  "title": "App Recommendation System with Explanations",
  "text": "The system provides app recommendations and corresponding explanations, which can be used by sales teams to engage with customers. The system consists of two main types of models: the relevance model for accuracy and the Diversity and Explanation (DAE) models for diversity and explainability.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "System Overview",
      "text": "The system is designed to provide app recommendations and corresponding explanations, which can be used by sales teams to engage with customers. The system consists of two main types of models: the relevance model for accuracy and the Diversity and Explanation (DAE) models for diversity and explainability."
    },
    {
      "title": "Relevance Model",
      "text": "The relevance model learns the similarity between a user and an item, which is used to generate app recommendations. The model takes into account various features of the user and the item, such as categorical features, continuous-valued features, and user installation history."
    },
    {
      "title": "Diversity and Explanation (DAE) Models",
      "text": "The DAE models are designed to control aggregate diversity and generate recommendation explanations. There are three types of DAE models: 'Hot' for extracting popular items, 'Categorical' for categorical features, and 'Continuous' for continuous-valued features."
    },
    {
      "title": "Experiments",
      "text": "The system was evaluated on a private enterprise app recommendation dataset using metrics such as hit ratio and NDCG. The results showed that the system performed better than other approaches in terms of accuracy, diversity, and explainability."
    },
    {
      "title": "Impact",
      "text": "The system has been deployed as a service for sales teams at Salesforce, and user studies have shown positive feedback from users. The system enables sales teams to explore unpopular but relevant apps and understand why such apps are recommended, which can improve sales revenue."
    }
  ]
}

