{
  "title": "Revolutionizing the Experience Industry: Lessons from Launching an AI-Assisted Content Creation Feature",
  "authors": [
    {
      "name": "Agus"
    },
    {
      "name": "Raslam"
    },
    {
      "name": "Konrad"
    }
  ],
  "abstract": "In this article, we share our journey of launching an AI-assisted content creation feature that impacted both the supply and demand side of the market. We highlight key learnings from our multi-quarter feature launch, including the importance of perseverance in convictions, being data-driven, collaborative communication, central knowledge repositories, early analytics involvement, meticulous attention to detail, and anticipating potential issues.",
  "keywords": [
    "AI-assisted content creation",
    "experience industry",
    "data-driven approach",
    "collaborative communication",
    "central knowledge repositories"
  ],
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Introduction",
      "text": "In recent days, AI has been the talk of the town. However, integrating it into a product is far from straightforward."
    },
    {
      "title": "The Curveball",
      "text": "Our first experiment showed that our primary success metric was significantly lower than expected. Our treatment group lagged behind the control group."
    },
    {
      "title": "The Win",
      "text": "Ahead of the second test, we made a few UX improvements based on our learnings. We clarified that the AI page was a step within the normal product creation wizard..."
    },
    {
      "title": "What Led to Our Success",
      "text": "Our key learnings from this multi-quarter feature launch are summarized below: Have perseverance in your convictions, being data-driven is key, collaborative communication is essential, central knowledge repositories and singular source of truth databases are crucial..."
    },
    {
      "title": "Conclusion",
      "text": "While AI has undoubtedly been the talk of the town in recent days, integrating it into a product is far from straightforward."
    }
  ]
}

