      "As Customer Zero, we pave the way by being an early adopter of our own technology, getting learnings, and working with the product development lifecycle to drill those learnings back into the product. In many cases, we’re sprinting ahead of the product.",
      "We want to partner with you on your road to becoming an agentic enterprise. We promise to continue to share our Customer Zero journey to help you make this critical leap for your own company.",
